title: Hackney Fresh
description: Whole foods all-organic store and small take-away. Take-away offers coffee, 2 soups of the day (generally vegan), sandwiches and savory crepes (vegan options). The store has a great choice of vegan meat substitutes, organic fruit and veggies, breads, spices, flours, vegan chocolates, as well as vegan cosmetics and more.
